{"tid":421721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好人好事]原來呢個世界仲有好心人","createTime":"2017-10-02T13:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T13:34:01.000Z","uid":147485,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"224df6ec822c3b009264e0acedb92d57b1c3f8c5","tid":421721,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日小弟下晝搭巴士果時就唔小心留左個銀包係架車到<br />\n去到係食完晚飯先發現到 諗住今翅仆街鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係點都好 小弟都搏一搏打左去巴士站果邊問先<br />\n佢話冇執到小弟個銀包 然後我就死死地氣打去銀行搞報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知報失完張卡 就收到電話話執到小弟個銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我都諗住卡又報失左 其他野係到就算啦 現金冇左當破財擋災<br />\n即刻9秒9沖左落去巴士站到拎番個銀包都好<br />\n最後落到去拎番個銀包一check 全部野都係晒到<br />\n連CASH都係到一個崩都冇少到<br />\n<br />\n係到小弟要多謝執到我個銀包仲要冇拎到入面D野既好心人士/車長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然入面既錢唔係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358b4d5ae7daa32c56186d62acd7ba9ab0af8eb6","tid":421721,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"機會少過5%<br />\n你真係好好彩"},{"pid":"aafa2fe62a79bde566ac4c03d75d61ad97cb9bdb","tid":421721,"uid":75246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"今次算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次自己小心啦"},{"pid":"faf1fecbae50e8ed38c6b75030fbdd76863c1f1e","tid":421721,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機會少過5%<br />\n你真係好好彩</blockquote><br />\n真係好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身打定輸數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj